data.description: Welcome to this stunning Martha Stewart inspired home in the beautiful Hampton Oaks Subdivision. This 4-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath resale home is a true gem with so much to offer. As you arrive, you'll be captivated by the beautifully landscaped yard and impeccable curb appeal. Step inside to find a spacious Living Room/Dining Room combo featuring luxury vinyl hardwood floors throughout the entire main level. Every light fixture in this property has been thoughtfully replaced to enhance the ambiance. Enjoy the convenience of a dedicated Home Office space on the main level, along with a Powder Room. The spacious fireside Family Room features custom built-in bookcases and cabinetry flanking either side of the gas fireplace. The adjacent gourmet Kitchen has been completely renovated with custom built-in cabinetry, an island with ample storage, stainless steel appliances, stunning quartz countertops, and a beautiful subway tile backsplash. A very spacious Breakfast Area leads directly to the rear yard with an oversized patio, perfect for outdoor entertainment! The second story boasts a generous Primary Suite with a large Sitting Area and an oversized walk-in closet. The primary bathroom has also been updated with beautiful tile, a separate shower, garden tub, and a double sink vanity. Additionally, there's a large loft space on the second story for reading, relaxing, or watching television. Three additional secondary bedrooms are beautifully appointed, and the hall bath has been updated with new tile and cabinetry. Additionally, there is a convenient laundry room with a sink. The Hampton Oaks Subdivision offers resort-like amenities, a dreamy neighborhood entrance setting the tone for a serene and welcoming community, including a renovated barn area, a clubhouse, a community garden, swimming pool, lighted tennis courts, and a playground. This incredible home won't last long, so don't miss the opportunity to make it yours.
